{"tid":1813147,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【天滅中共】蘇州老街地陷涼亭下沉　商店及住戶緊急搬走","createTime":"2020-01-06T05:05:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-06T06:34:39.000Z","uid":244704,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ef6ffa977bf0563998d377280ad2568632554114","tid":1813147,"uid":244704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T05:05:48.000Z","msg":"[img]//<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20200106/photo/bkn-20200106090111439-0106_00952_001_01b.jpg?20200106122127[/img]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20200106%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200106090111439-0106_00952_001_01b.jpg%3F20200106122127%5B%2Fimg%5D&d=bwUHcV0Pscj1NrVo4Cy%2FDYgDU6S0x1vJ5b5MQMl6fZo%3D&h=50155c21\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20200106/photo/bkn-20200106090111439-0106_00952_001_01b.jpg?20200106122127[/img]</a><br />\n內地近期不時傳地陷新聞，位於江蘇省蘇州滄浪區的十全街，上周六（4日）也出現路陷。目前臨街的商店及住戶基於安全考慮均已搬走，現場亦被封鎖，有人員巡查。據指路陷疑與河道清淤有關。<br />\n<br />\n網上片段所見，一段仿古長廊全面塌陷，地磚裂開下沉，部分沿河牆壁同樣裂開。有目擊者表示，看到一座涼亭「慢慢的變矮」，並聽到轟轟聲。蘇州市交通管理局周日（5日）表示，上周六接報十全街「蘇州飯店」北面公共巴士站發生坍塌，經現場調查，事發地點是一座仿古式休憩長廊。 通報又稱，此次塌陷是因道路北面的河道清淤工程導致駁岸塌陷，塌陷區距離巴士站約50厘米。<br />\n<br />\n十全街位於蘇州城區東南部，全長約2000米，街上有著名的南林飯店、南園賓館和古典園林網師園，國畫大師張大千、張善子等也曾寓居於此。據說十全街已有千年歷史，因從前當地有十古井，因而取名「十泉街」。後來清朝乾隆皇南巡蘇州，才改名為「十全街」。<br />\n<br />\n[img]//<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20200106/photo/bkn-20200106090111439-0106_00952_001_02b.jpg?20200106122127[/img]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20200106%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200106090111439-0106_00952_001_02b.jpg%3F20200106122127%5B%2Fimg%5D&d=bwUHcV0Pscj1NrVo4Cy%2FDYgDU6S0x1vJ5b5MQMl6fZo%3D&h=8f8712c7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20200106/photo/bkn-20200106090111439-0106_00952_001_02b.jpg?20200106122127[/img]</a><br />\n[img]//<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20200106/photo/bkn-20200106090111439-0106_00952_001_03b.jpg?20200106122127[/img]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20200106%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200106090111439-0106_00952_001_03b.jpg%3F20200106122127%5B%2Fimg%5D&d=bwUHcV0Pscj1NrVo4Cy%2FDYgDU6S0x1vJ5b5MQMl6fZo%3D&h=73d9d55a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20200106/photo/bkn-20200106090111439-0106_00952_001_03b.jpg?20200106122127[/img]</a><br />\n[img]//<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20200106/photo/bkn-20200106090111439-0106_00952_001_04b.jpg?20200106122127[/img]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20200106%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200106090111439-0106_00952_001_04b.jpg%3F20200106122127%5B%2Fimg%5D&d=bwUHcV0Pscj1NrVo4Cy%2FDYgDU6S0x1vJ5b5MQMl6fZo%3D&h=ebd2894a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20200106/photo/bkn-20200106090111439-0106_00952_001_04b.jpg?20200106122127[/img]</a><br />\n[img]//<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20200106/photo/bkn-20200106090111439-0106_00952_001_05b.jpg?20200106122127[/img]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20200106%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200106090111439-0106_00952_001_05b.jpg%3F20200106122127%5B%2Fimg%5D&d=bwUHcV0Pscj1NrVo4Cy%2FDYgDU6S0x1vJ5b5MQMl6fZo%3D&h=178c4ed7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20200106/photo/bkn-20200106090111439-0106_00952_001_05b.jpg?20200106122127[/img]</a>"},{"pid":"f4b731ccdb170af1ad56e5e07b596bf625f860cf","tid":1813147,"uid":134415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T05:06:35.000Z","msg":"GDP"},{"pid":"9f30285ecebd773e809d6f8f4ad3b6ea56ceb67a","tid":1813147,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T06:34:39.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n中資禍港數十年，若不肅清，真香港人恐將不復存在<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1810669\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1810669</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}